dct_description_sm: Map series of Burma. Relief shown by contours, form lines, hachures ans spot heights. Map shows international, provincial or state, district or tribal boundaries, roads, railways. Sheets lack uniform title. Each sheet has a number, area covered and district names. Includes index to sheets. Set contains various editions, some provisional, and photocopies.
